originalText.text: Dr. Paige is so incredible. I started seeing her in New York and fly to see her in Nashville now - she is so amazing!! She helped me recover after ankle surgery and continues to help me today with anxiety and migraines through acupuncture.  Can’t say enough good things about her practice. Her clinic is so peaceful and zen-like.  I always feel better after leaving. Every acupuncture treatment is more helpful than the last. I highly recommend Shen Medicine to anyone in Nashville!
